2026-05-16 11:32:32,628 | INFO | tenantai | main.py:52 | save_message() | message_query - {'type': 'message', 'session_id': '1e8c220d-a033-4831-bce8-a78315e4a083', 'tenant_id': '1', 'tenant_brand_id': '3', 'brand_tone': 'PROFESSIONAL', 'sender': 'Bot', 'message': 'I\'d be happy to explain how Remindly works.\n\nRemindly is a smart reminder assistant that uses a simple chat interaction to help you schedule tasks, manage daily activities, and receive timely push notifications. Here\'s a step-by-step overview of how it works:\n\n1. **Open the Remindly chat widget**: You can access Remindly through our chat interface.\n2. **Type a reminder request**: Simply type a reminder request in the chat window, such as "Remind me to attend the team meeting tomorrow at 10 AM."\n3. **The chatbot confirms the reminder details**: Our chatbot will understand the task title and reminder time, and confirm the details with you.\n4. **The reminder gets scheduled automatically**: Once confirmed, the reminder will be scheduled automatically.\n5. **A notification is sent at the scheduled time**: At the specified time, you\'ll receive a push notification reminding you of the task.\n\nThat\'s it! Remindly makes it easy to create reminders, manage tasks, and stay on top of your daily activities. If you have any questions or need further assistance, feel free to ask.', 'event': 'BOT_MESSAGE', 'token_used': 1375, 'timestamp': '2026-05-16T11:32:32.620692'}
