ble PDF. You can save this PDF to your computer or share it with others.\n\nThat's it! The PDF Generator application is designed to be easy to use, and it provides a clean and user-friendly interface that allows quick access to conversion tools without requiring technical knowledge.\n\nIf you have any questions or need further assistance, feel free to ask.\n\nWould you like to know more about the main features of the PDF Generator application or how to use it for specific file types?", 'event': 'BOT_MESSAGE', 'token_used': 1478, 'timestamp': '2026-05-23T10:10:07.573574'}
