2026-05-26 15:35:48,671 | INFO | tenantai | main.py:51 | save_message() | Received from topic STORE_MESSAGE_KAFKA_TOPIC - {'type': 'message', 'session_id': 'ff7c13fe-bea6-4b6e-81fd-8f12fa3cfc98', 'tenant_id': '1', 'tenant_brand_id': '10', 'brand_tone': 'PROFESSIONAL', 'sender': 'Bot', 'message': 'To apply for admission to Greenfield Institute of Technology & Management, you can follow these steps:\n\n1. **Online Application**: You can submit your application online through our official website. Click on the "Admissions" tab and follow the link to the online application portal.\n2. **Direct Campus Counseling**: If you prefer a more personalized experience, you can schedule a direct campus counseling session with our admissions team. We\'ll guide you through the application process and answer any questions you may have.\n3. **Required Documents**: Make sure you have the following documents ready:\n\t* 10th and 12th mark sheets\n\t* Transfer certificate (TC)\n\t* ID proof (Aadhaar card, passport, etc.)\n\t* Photos\n\t* Community certificate (if applicable)\n\t* Entrance score card (if required)\n4. **Fill out the Application Form**: Carefully fill out the online application form, providing accurate and complete information.\n5. **Pay the Application Fee**: Pay the application fee online, which is non-refundable.\n6. **Submit the Application**: Once you\'ve completed the application form and paid the fee, submit it online or through direct campus counseling.\n7. **Wait for Verification**: Our admissions team will verify your application and documents. You may be contacted for additional information or clarification.\n8. **Admission Decision**: After verification, we\'ll inform you of our admission decision. If accepted, you\'ll receive a provisional admission offer.\n\nIf you have any questions or need help with the application process, feel free to ask, and I\'ll be happy to assist you.', 'event': 'BOT_MESSAGE', 'token_used': 1522, 'timestamp': '2026-05-26T15:35:48.662